HEADWORD: Whencesoever
<hw>Whence`so*ev"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv. & conj.</pos> <def>From
what place soever; from what cause or source soever.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Any idea, <qex>whencesoever</qex> we have it.</q>
